text: Eva Lagrange (born 17 April 1993) is a German-Swedish speed skater. She was Swedish champion in 2014 and 2015 with a huge lead at the Swedish all-round championship. In 2015, she also won the Swedish Sprint Championship. She competed at the 2015 European Speed Skating Championships. == References == Category:1993 births Category:Swedish speed skaters Category:Living people
